WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.326
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.326 --> 00:00:03.055
Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:03.340 --> 00:00:17.075
We are going to start praying more and more; that's what the Lord has told me to do and he told Diana to do the same thing.

00:00:30.229 --> 00:00:30.494
It's not really prophetic; some of the things I see, I feel like they're warnings.

00:00:30.494 --> 00:00:51.740
As watchmen and watchwomen and men of God, we're watchmen and we are going to start praying against some of the things that the Lord has showed us.

00:00:51.740 --> 00:01:05.133
It's not just to tell you about it and just go, 'Hey, sound the alarm,' and then do nothing about it.

00:01:13.880 --> 00:01:14.050
We're called to change things, and prayer—that's our whole slogan: Prayer Changes Things.

00:01:14.050 --> 00:01:34.327
We believe in the power of prayer and we got our first picture today in the mail because we told you all to send your pictures to us so we could pray over your families.

00:01:34.327 --> 00:01:41.640
Whatever you are believing God for, write on the back of the picture.

00:01:41.640 --> 00:01:47.979
Diana and I will pray over it right now.

00:01:47.979 --> 00:02:09.520
Write on the back, 'Hey, we do not want this shown,' or, 'It's okay to share the picture,' because some people don't want to be all over the internet.

00:02:09.520 --> 00:02:17.005
But we're going to pray for this family today.

00:02:17.005 --> 00:02:35.469
Her husband's dressed up in a tuxedo, and they look like they're at a wedding; they look nice, a very classy family.

00:02:35.469 --> 00:02:49.545
This woman says that her son is wayward and he is not talking to the family anymore.

00:02:49.545 --> 00:03:16.090
It sounds like a pretty rough situation, but we're going to believe God that he's going to turn around, that he's coming home, and this wayward son is going to be on fire for Jesus.

00:03:31.680 --> 00:03:40.249
The enemy is after the young people because they are going to be the forerunners of this great revival that's about to take place.

00:03:40.249 --> 00:04:02.985
When we go to these places and drive around, I have an urgency for the college kids because I know what God is about to do on these campuses.

00:04:02.985 --> 00:04:15.046
Someone mailed me something that showed some of the college campuses having revivals.

00:04:18.092 --> 00:04:23.440
It was all over several college campuses; they're having major baptisms, salvations, and altar calls.

00:04:23.440 --> 00:04:27.080
Amazing stuff is going on.

00:04:27.080 --> 00:04:34.034
I believe we're seeing the first fruits that will start to spring up.

00:04:34.034 --> 00:04:47.840
He told me March, April, and May that we would start to see the first fruits of the outpouring of the finances.

00:04:47.840 --> 00:04:54.447
It's already been a major thing that happened Friday.

00:04:55.468 --> 00:05:09.386
Now some people say that was a big nothingburger, but folks, we have a president that is pro-crypto, saying that we want to have a Bitcoin reserve.

00:05:14.711 --> 00:05:17.555
The last administration was trying to sue everybody and the SEC was after everything.

00:05:21.480 --> 00:05:34.871
It sounds to me like we have, for the first time, an administration saying, 'Hey, we want to join this new platform of new technology.

00:05:34.871 --> 00:05:41.205
' That in itself is a miracle.

00:05:41.205 --> 00:05:59.120
Without having some kind of big windfall of a financial outpouring, we see the foundation being laid for the wealth of the sinner laid up for the righteous.

00:05:59.120 --> 00:06:11.400
We're seeing the first blades: we have the blade, then the ear, then the full manifestation, and then the crop—the huge field of harvest.

00:06:17.251 --> 00:06:25.966
It has to start somewhere, and I believe we just saw a little blade poke up out of the dirt saying, 'Hello, I'm here.

00:06:25.966 --> 00:06:31.072
' That should get you excited.

00:06:31.072 --> 00:06:51.023
The last administration with Elizabeth Warren—she doesn't like crypto and she's like, 'We're going to stop it, we're going to destroy it.

00:06:51.023 --> 00:07:00.968
' Here we have President Trump saying, 'Let's make America great again.

00:07:00.968 --> 00:07:07.098
' It is something to look forward to.

00:07:07.098 --> 00:07:15.840
At least 'Pocahontas' might be quiet for a little bit in the SEC.

00:07:15.840 --> 00:07:21.980
Praise the Lord, it is what it is, Diana.

00:07:21.980 --> 00:07:25.627
These people are evil.

00:07:25.627 --> 00:07:32.568
They can't even stand up for a cancer patient.

00:07:33.421 --> 00:07:35.715
God help them all.

00:07:35.715 --> 00:07:42.040
Well, we're going to pray now.

00:07:42.040 --> 00:07:52.813
The Lord said, 'Make five minutes, don't sit here and ramble on.

00:07:52.813 --> 00:08:08.360
' So we're going to make it just five minutes of talking and we're going to do a lot of praying.

00:08:08.360 --> 00:08:10.844
Let's get praying.

00:08:10.844 --> 00:08:15.884
We're going to take communion with y'all.

00:08:15.884 --> 00:08:21.780
We're going into the throne room of God.

00:08:21.780 --> 00:08:32.696
This is what we do in this household: we never enter into prayer without taking communion first.

00:08:32.696 --> 00:08:44.950
I'm showing what is mine is God's and what's God's is mine.

00:08:44.950 --> 00:09:00.305
Everything he has provided for me, I receive it by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of our testimony.

00:09:00.305 --> 00:09:23.640
He has redeemed us, he set us free, and we enter into his throne boldly because of his son's blood and what he did for us on that beautiful cross.

00:09:38.700 --> 00:09:39.014
Thank you to whoever sent these communion cups to us from Amazon.

00:09:39.014 --> 00:09:45.880
You sent us two boxes; it's a blessing.

00:09:45.880 --> 00:09:56.580
Father, we take this body right now in the name of Jesus.

00:09:56.580 --> 00:10:10.880
If you just have a cracker, it's good; people say that's disrespectful, but God knows your heart.

00:10:10.880 --> 00:10:18.550
I'll take a potato chip, whatever I can, just to get close to the Father.

00:10:19.525 --> 00:10:23.935
It's what it represents in your heart.

00:10:23.935 --> 00:10:29.440
I come before him boldly.

00:10:29.440 --> 00:10:35.720
If it's a piece of bread or whatever, don't be religious; just look at him and say, 'Jesus, I want to be close to you.

00:10:35.720 --> 00:10:48.120
I want to know you more than I know my past memories.

00:10:48.120 --> 00:10:50.800
I'm desperate for change.

00:10:50.800 --> 00:11:26.179
' Some people can't afford much, but if you do this daily and you seek him daily, and you sow when he tells you to sow, and you give, and it shall be given unto you—good measure, pressed down, shaken together, and running over, will men give into your bosom.

00:11:26.179 --> 00:11:40.620
I believe he said in Malachi that he would rebuke the devourer for your sake, even if it's just a penny.

00:11:40.620 --> 00:11:48.611
I believe what he says more than I believe my circumstances.

00:11:48.611 --> 00:12:08.491
Regardless of what I have in the bank, the Bible says that I'll be the lender and not the borrower—that I will be able to lend to the nations.

00:12:08.491 --> 00:12:14.400
To be able to lend to a nation is substantial.

00:12:16.464 --> 00:12:29.075
It needs to be hundreds of millions of dollars in the bank to say, 'I'm a lender to nations.

00:12:29.075 --> 00:12:48.700
' The United States gives money to people, and you think about how much money that is—it's billions.

00:12:48.700 --> 00:12:57.954
That's exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:12:57.954 --> 00:13:02.773
But how do you start there?

00:13:16.239 --> 00:13:17.199
You start with a seed, and a seed brings forth increase: some thirty, some sixty, and some hundredfold.

00:13:17.199 --> 00:13:21.129
It's all in the ground you're sowing into.

00:13:21.129 --> 00:13:27.425
If you're sowing into bad ground, don't expect a big harvest.

00:13:27.425 --> 00:13:39.795
A farmer doesn't sow into bad ground; he sows into manure or fertilized ground that's going to reap back.

00:13:39.795 --> 00:13:45.384
So that's what we're going to do today.

00:13:45.384 --> 00:13:51.155
Now Father, I thank you for their ground.

00:13:56.949 --> 00:14:00.524
I thank you that whatever they put their hands to will prosper.

00:14:00.524 --> 00:14:14.800
Father, we take authority over the spirit of poverty, lack, not enough, and barely getting by.

00:14:20.097 --> 00:14:30.173
We break your stronghold off of them in the name of Jesus and we say: let go of their money now in Jesus' name.

00:14:39.920 --> 00:14:49.217
Father, I thank you that you said you would provide everything according to your riches and glory by Christ Jesus.

00:14:49.217 --> 00:14:52.668
All our needs are met.

00:15:05.660 --> 00:15:05.990
Father, we thank you that it's not just about finances, it's about our health.

00:15:06.649 --> 00:15:15.107
You took it all on the cross for us.

00:15:17.133 --> 00:15:27.737
The chastisement of our peace was upon you and with your stripes we're healed.

00:15:27.737 --> 00:15:32.440
Lord, we take up this body right now.

00:15:49.300 --> 00:16:00.420
You were wounded for our transgressions and bruised for our iniquities, and we believe we receive today all the ills that as we take this body into our body, we're healed, whole, and well in the name of Jesus.

00:16:00.420 --> 00:16:13.314
Now Lord, you said to make much of the blood and the blood will make much of you.

00:16:13.314 --> 00:16:21.890
We plead the blood of Jesus over our families and over our sins.

00:16:21.890 --> 00:16:32.383
We thank you that the blood washes it all away today.

00:16:32.383 --> 00:16:45.493
When we confess our sins, you're faithful and just to forgive us and cleanse us from all unrighteousness.

00:16:45.493 --> 00:16:59.400
We plead the blood of Jesus from the top of our head to the soles of our feet.

00:16:59.400 --> 00:17:08.865
Take communion the way you like; there's no right or wrong way, there's only seeking Jesus.

00:17:08.865 --> 00:17:12.812
Find a relationship, not religion.

00:17:12.812 --> 00:17:20.703
So, Father, we lift up Christian before you right now.

00:17:20.703 --> 00:17:24.863
Christian, you're coming home in Jesus' name.

00:17:30.390 --> 00:17:31.457
We speak for this family to be reunited.

00:17:31.457 --> 00:17:37.480
Satan, take your hands off Christian and his family.

00:17:37.480 --> 00:17:57.244
I thank you, Father, that you've called us to the kingdom for such a time as this to pray over the ones that are lost and wayward.

00:17:57.244 --> 00:18:21.943
As a point of contact for all the other ones on this channel who are wayward, we're believing with you right now that Satan has to let go of those unsaved loved ones right now.

00:18:32.249 --> 00:18:32.559
We call them into the kingdom of God.

00:18:47.943 --> 00:18:48.234
I thank you that their eyes are no longer blinded by the demonic.

00:18:48.234 --> 00:18:57.600
This will be a time of a great turnaround in families.

00:18:57.600 --> 00:19:09.185
We bind these demonic spirits off the families and say you will go thus far and no further.

00:19:15.940 --> 00:19:17.739
We call for a turnaround in your marriages, your children, and your grandchildren.

00:19:20.571 --> 00:19:23.737
Father, I thank you for healings over their bodies.

00:19:23.737 --> 00:19:36.992
This is the time not to be always looking for tomorrow, but to look for today.

00:19:50.572 --> 00:19:50.799
Our marriages are going to be strong and blessed.

00:19:58.570 --> 00:20:02.540
We bind strife in Jesus' name.

00:20:08.575 --> 00:20:13.120
We thank you that there is great love and peace in these homes.

00:20:13.120 --> 00:20:31.604
Children will be raised up in a godly way and when they get older, they will not depart from it.

00:20:31.604 --> 00:20:56.737
I thank you, Father, that the men will rise up to be the spiritual backbone of the home; they will be the Davids who go after the giants and slay them.

00:21:02.970 --> 00:21:16.980
We have the Esthers rising up, and the Hannahs, to be the Proverbs 31 women—not having a Jezebel spirit or a Delilah spirit, but being a support mate to that husband.

00:21:16.980 --> 00:21:31.630
These men and women of God will join together in unity to bring in this great harvest.

00:21:31.630 --> 00:21:40.284
We will serve the Lord with all our heart, mind, soul, and strength.

00:21:40.284 --> 00:21:59.775
If my people who are called by my name will humble themselves and pray and turn from their wicked ways, then you said you would hear from heaven and heal our land.

00:22:00.898 --> 00:22:06.640
We're coming back to you bolder and stronger than we've ever been before.

00:22:06.640 --> 00:22:14.229
I thank you for a supernatural turnaround in this nation.

00:22:14.229 --> 00:22:23.983
Father, we come before you boldly and ask that you give President Trump wisdom.

00:22:32.213 --> 00:22:32.479
We pray for him and for JD Vance.

00:22:33.819 --> 00:22:44.360
We pray for our leaders, for the new German leader, the South Korean leaders, and for Canada's leader.

00:22:49.302 --> 00:22:53.960
Father, I thank you that Justin Trudeau is removed in Jesus' name.

00:22:53.960 --> 00:23:04.212
His days of being in power are over; he would resign and move out of the way.

00:23:17.400 --> 00:23:19.766
I thank you that a godly leader would rise up in Canada to lead that nation from sea to sea.

00:23:34.720 --> 00:23:34.992
We even thank you for Uganda's president.

00:23:36.782 --> 00:23:54.760
We believe for President Trump to be protected from the north, south, east, and west; there are angels watching over him.

00:23:54.760 --> 00:24:01.982
Give him supernatural wisdom on how to deal this crypto out.

00:24:01.982 --> 00:24:12.549
We call forth that wealth transfer right now in the name of Jesus.

00:24:12.549 --> 00:24:14.940
There's no more delay.

00:24:14.940 --> 00:24:17.284
Fund the harvest!

00:24:17.284 --> 00:24:23.840
Satan, take your hands off of this crypto.

00:24:24.160 --> 00:24:29.470
We pray over the Iraqi dinar; we call you to reinstate and revalue right now.

00:24:29.700 --> 00:24:48.630
We call gold and silver to soar to the highest prices we've ever seen to bring forth a supernatural wealth transfer and creative ideas to get wealth.

00:24:50.350 --> 00:24:58.559
We seek you today, Father, and we will hear the Good Shepherd's voice.

00:24:58.559 --> 00:25:06.440
We thank you for creative ideas and that you would anoint our hands.

00:25:18.600 --> 00:25:19.035
Whatever we put our hands to will prosper.

00:25:21.210 --> 00:25:27.506
We are the head and not the tail; we're above and not beneath.

00:25:27.506 --> 00:25:33.844
We're going to come out of the pit.

00:25:45.080 --> 00:25:45.880
Now faith is the substance of things hoped for and evidence of things not seen.

00:25:45.880 --> 00:25:51.680
We call those things around right now.

00:25:51.680 --> 00:26:15.059
Our businesses would flourish, whether that's being the greatest pie maker, burger maker, barbecue maker, or a janitor service—be the greatest because we give you the glory.

00:26:15.059 --> 00:26:29.350
I'm anointed to be a janitor, a banker, or a businesswoman, all for the glory of God.

00:26:29.350 --> 00:26:39.547
Not for our own pride or lust, but all for you, Lord.

00:26:55.279 --> 00:26:59.009
To be the best race car driver, the best movie star, or the best football player—all to the glory of God.

00:26:59.009 --> 00:27:05.423
Fame doesn't change us; popularity doesn't change us.

00:27:05.423 --> 00:27:18.926
We are changed only by the blood of the Lamb and the word of our testimony.

00:27:18.926 --> 00:27:32.164
We're changed from glory to glory to be who you've called us to be.

00:27:32.164 --> 00:27:37.526
Create in us a clean heart.

00:27:53.782 --> 00:27:54.013
We are filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit today.

00:28:08.268 --> 00:28:08.605
I was going to pray for people dealing with childhood trauma from your past.

00:28:08.605 --> 00:28:22.593
If you're an adult and you have dealt with abuse, especially from your father, we come before you right now.

00:28:22.593 --> 00:28:24.856
Say this right now: 'My father loves me.

00:28:24.856 --> 00:28:34.947
' Your earthly father may have missed the mark, but your heavenly Father didn't.

00:28:34.947 --> 00:28:46.000
One second in his presence can erase decades of mental abuse and strongholds.

00:28:54.199 --> 00:28:54.499
Father, I thank you that they are free in Jesus' name.

00:28:54.499 --> 00:28:58.680
Be free, be whole, be healed.

00:28:58.680 --> 00:29:05.129
Your heavenly Father is chasing after you and you cannot run away from it.

00:29:05.129 --> 00:29:13.616
No more victim mentality; we are victors and overcomers.

00:29:13.616 --> 00:29:29.000
Your dad may have been a bad man who beat or molested you, but we forgive them—not for them, but for you.

00:29:31.999 --> 00:29:37.700
I release that so I am not taking that into my tomorrow.

00:29:43.279 --> 00:29:44.649
I surrender my pain to you, God.

00:29:44.649 --> 00:30:00.240
When you take your hand out of trying to fix it, you let God take over.

00:30:00.240 --> 00:30:10.097
One moment with the Holy Spirit can change decades of childhood trauma.

00:30:10.571 --> 00:30:15.388
The anointing is the burden-removing, yoke-destroying power of God.

00:30:15.388 --> 00:30:22.457
We're expecting a great turnaround in your lives today.

00:30:22.457 --> 00:30:24.120
Hope!

00:30:24.120 --> 00:30:29.140
We're anchored to hope.

00:30:29.140 --> 00:30:34.909
I know in whom I've believed.

00:30:39.799 --> 00:30:45.760
God has a great future for every single one of you.

00:30:45.760 --> 00:31:00.370
He says, 'I wish above all things that you prosper and be in health, even as your soul prospers.

00:31:00.370 --> 00:31:11.771
' As Oral Roberts said, 'God is a good God and the devil's a bad devil.

00:31:11.771 --> 00:31:22.159
' When you go through trials, always stay on God's side.

00:31:23.180 --> 00:31:26.360
Your goodness is running after me.

00:31:26.360 --> 00:31:41.300
All my life you have been faithful; all my life you have been so, so good.

00:31:41.300 --> 00:31:48.749
With every breath that I am able, I will sing of the goodness of God.

00:32:01.599 --> 00:32:01.919
Your mercy is running after me.

00:32:04.679 --> 00:32:17.182
If you ever have a song come into your spirit like that, just sing it, because there's breakthrough that happens with praise and worship.

00:32:21.140 --> 00:32:22.853
When praises go up, blessings come down.

00:32:31.180 --> 00:32:38.004
I had a breakthrough recently from singing a song the Holy Spirit brought to me.

00:32:38.004 --> 00:32:56.469
We're real people with real needs, and we have to stand and resist the devil.

00:33:10.999 --> 00:33:17.880
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, stop being lazy just because you're on YouTube.

00:33:17.880 --> 00:33:37.777
Stand up, put your big boy pants on, and do what you know to do.

00:33:37.777 --> 00:34:06.080
' You may say, 'I can't sing like Celine Dion or Carrie Underwood,' but just make a joyful noise.

00:34:06.820 --> 00:34:27.826
I don't have the right pitch a lot of times either, but he visits it.

00:34:27.826 --> 00:34:50.140
Use whatever you've been given to the glory of God.

00:34:50.140 --> 00:34:58.634
It's all about Jesus today.

00:34:58.634 --> 00:35:49.960
Ninety-nine percent of the time, I don't have a clue of the words; I'll just make them up even if it just sounds like I say our heart.

00:35:49.960 --> 00:35:55.537
Yeah, those words.

00:35:55.537 --> 00:36:17.480
And I go, 'I don't know if that was right.

00:36:17.480 --> 00:36:32.514
' Even with that song I just sang, I don't know if I sang all those words right, but I tried.

00:36:32.514 --> 00:36:38.650
I just say, 'It is what it is.

00:36:38.650 --> 00:36:55.314
' But He knows your heart, and He is up there going, 'Well, you know, you sang that a little off-key.

00:36:55.314 --> 00:37:01.460
' It doesn't matter; He just loves you.

00:37:01.460 --> 00:37:07.440
He's chasing after you; His mercy is running after you.

00:37:09.120 --> 00:37:22.090
It is so important—I'll say it again like I said last time—that you have those stacking rocks experiences with the Lord.

00:37:22.090 --> 00:37:27.786
Stack the rocks; every single rock means something.

00:37:27.786 --> 00:37:36.194
How many times has God showed up and showed off in your life?

00:37:38.166 --> 00:37:46.360
And we forget the things that He delivered us from yesterday, and we go, 'Oh, I don't remember when God did something for me.

00:37:46.360 --> 00:37:53.380
' But He may have done something five years ago.

00:38:00.915 --> 00:38:05.292
You should always go back to what He's done in the past and never take it for granted.

00:38:05.292 --> 00:38:16.599
Say, 'God, You came through for me at such-and-such a time, and You'll do it again.

00:38:16.599 --> 00:38:27.007
' And that song is perfect for that because you're saying, 'All my life, You have been faithful.

00:38:27.007 --> 00:38:37.453
' And as you sing that, think about all the times that He's come through.

00:38:37.453 --> 00:38:43.413
He'll do it again.

00:38:46.986 --> 00:38:54.535
Just take a look at where you are and where you've been.

00:38:54.535 --> 00:39:00.883
Hasn't He always come through for you?

00:39:00.883 --> 00:39:06.119
He's the same as He was way back then.

00:39:06.119 --> 00:39:14.465
You may not know how, you may not know when, but He'll do it again.

00:39:15.405 --> 00:39:15.847
Do you believe it?

00:39:16.676 --> 00:39:17.713
I believe it today.

00:39:19.756 --> 00:39:32.200
It's important that you don't lose sight of your last miracle and always give Him praise for it on a day-to-day basis.

00:39:48.666 --> 00:39:49.115
I remember when Megan was not potty trained.

00:40:03.496 --> 00:40:10.667
I remember when we didn't have enough food to eat and we were at our last dollar, and we said, 'How are we going to get through our tomorrow?

00:40:10.667 --> 00:40:13.720
' And He came through.

00:40:16.827 --> 00:40:21.768
But God, who is rich in mercy, is merciful, and His mercy is new every morning.

00:40:22.093 --> 00:40:27.500
And He is good, and His mercy endures forever.

00:40:39.025 --> 00:40:44.520
And we choose to praise Him even in the valley of the shadow of death.

00:41:04.095 --> 00:41:04.359
I will fear no evil, for You are with me; Thy rod and Thy staff, they comfort me.

00:41:04.359 --> 00:41:21.968
Surely goodness and mercy will follow me all the days of my life, and I will rejoice in the house of the Lord forever.

00:41:21.968 --> 00:41:30.596
I rejoice with Him, for He is good and His mercy endures forever.

00:41:51.760 --> 00:41:52.440
For He is good—guess what they're going to say?

00:42:20.347 --> 00:42:25.857
You've got to say it, but you say it with all your heart today: 'For the Lord is good, and His mercy endures forever.

00:42:25.857 --> 00:42:55.040
' In every area of my life, in every circumstance of my life, I choose to give God glory, honor, and praise today.

